Package: SpotGraphs
Title: Generate igraph Objects With Visium Spot Coordinates For Basic Analysis Tasks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Alex", "Lee", , "alee262@jhmi.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1825-2439")),
      person("David", "Sanin", , "david.sanin@jhu.edu", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0188-7267")))
Description: Use x,y coordinates from 10X Visium data to create an igraph object, which 
    can be useful to identify which spots are immediately neighboring each other and to
    provide a simple, lightweight framework to work with spatial communities of spots.
